<title>Stand UP Together: An Action Guide</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body>
<h1 align="center">America Needs a Raise: An Action Guide </h1>
<p>If we're going to defeat the new Republican Congress'
destructive agenda, the labor movement and its allies will need
an army of activists in local communities to: </p>
<ul>
    <li>talk to their legislators; </li>
    <li>educate their co-workers on the issues; </li>
    <li>become politically active in voter registration and
        get-out-the-vote campaigns; </li>
    <li>organize and participate in pro-worker and union events
        and activities; </li>
    <li>build coalitions with others who care about the future of
        America and spread our message to the general public
        through local media. </li>
</ul>
<p>Success depends on our ability to mobilize and galvanize
support in every local community. If we fail, we will watch as
job protections and standards of living for American workers
continue to fall. But if we work together and succeed we can put
American back on track towards greater economic opportunity and
security for all its citizens.</p>
<p align="center"><a href="/index.htm">AFL-CIO Home Page</a> | <a
href="index.htm">America Needs a Raise Page</a></p>
<hr>
<p>Copyright &#169; AFL-CIO</p>
</body>
</html>
