    <p>Magazines </p>
    <p>Local Union Publications -- California Pride, SEIU Local
    1000; Unity, SEIU Local 250, Oakland, Calif.; Newsline 1999,
    UAW Local 1999. </p>
    <p>All Other Publication -- UNION, SEIU; AFSCME Public
    Employee, AFSCME; IBEW Journal, IBEW. </p>
    <p>Newsletters </p>
