http://aflcio.org:80/newsonline/96aug23/maritime.htm 204.127.237.106 19970215105844 text/html 10834
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 10:57:59 GMT
