<TITLE>Profile of Tian Jin University</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>Profile of Tianjin University</H2>
<P><IMG SRC="../image/truth.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE" ALT="[IMAGE]"> ~ Seeking Truth From Facts 
<PRE>
       
</PRE>
<HR>
<H3></H3>
<UL>
<LI><B>20</B><A HREF="deptidx.html"><B> </B></A><A HREF="deptidx.html">Departments Overview</A> 
<LI><B>22</B><A HREF="PhDprog.html"> Doctorate Programs</A> 
<LI><B>75</B><A HREF="MSTprog.html"><B> </B></A><A HREF="MSTprog.html">Masters</A><A HREF="PhDprog.html"> Programs</A><A HREF="MSTprog.html"> </A>
<LI><B>6</B><A HREF="keydisp.html"> Key</A><A HREF="PhDprog.html"> Programs</A><A HREF="keydisp.html"> </A>
<LI><B>5</B><B> </B><A HREF="keylab.html">Key Laboratories</A> 
<LI><B>14</B><A HREF="rscenter.html"> Research Institutes / Development Centers</A> 
<LI><A HREF="intstudy/introd.html">International Students Programs</A> 
</UL>
<HR>
<P><I>As a key university, Tianjin University now has an enrolment of 11,000 undergraduate students and about 2,000 graduate students. </I><BR>
 <I>Among 2,500 Faculty members, 1,000 are professors and associate professors.</I> 
</BODY>
