<Title> Celebrate the Centennial Anniversary of Tian Jin University</Title>
<center><IMG SRC="../image/peiyang.gif"></A></center><BR>
<center><A HREF = "../image/century.gif"><IMG SRC="../image/sma_cent.gif"></A></center><BR>
<pre><b>   On October 2, 1995 Tianjin University celebrated her 100th anniversary.
More than twenty thousand people attended the ceremony on Peiyang Square. 
President JIANG Zemin and Premier LI Peng sent their congratulation words. 
Vice-premier LI Lanqing gave cheerful speeches in the meeting on behalf of
the government.</p>
   A performance was given in the evening. Some famous actors and actresses 
of the nation showed up. More than ten thousand people watched the show.</b></p></pre>
<HR>
<PRE><A HREF = "../image/meeting.gif"><IMG SRC="../image/sm_meet.gif"
 ALT = "[IMAGE]"></A>    <A HREF="../image/square.gif"><IMG SRC="../image/sm_squa.gif"
