<TITLE>Tianjin Education and Research Network</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H3><STRONG>Tianjin Education and Research Network(TJERNET)</STRONG> </H3>
<P>TJERNET is supported by Tianjin Minicipal government to serve all the education and research institutes in Tianjin area, including Tianjin Economy Development Area(TEDA) and Tanggu area. 
<P>Tianjin is one of the largest cities in China. In Tianjin Area there are 24 colleges and universities, three military universities. There are also more than one 40 professional education institutes. These are, 
<P>
<P><A HREF="../index.html">Tianjin University</A> 
<P><A HREF="http://www.nankai.edu.cn">Nankai University</A> 
<P>Tianjin Medical University 
<P>Tianjin Normal University 
<P>Tianjin Science and Engineering Institute 
<P>Tianjin College of Finance and Economics 
<P>Tianjin College of Light Industry 
<P>Tianjin Textile Engineering Institute 
<P>Tianjin University of Commerce 
<P>Civil Aviation Institute of China 
<P>Tianjin Vocational and Technical Teachers' Training Institute 
<P>Tianjin Foreign Language Institute 
<P>Tianjin Traditional Chinese Medical Institute 
<P>Tianjin College of Agriculture 
<P>Tianjin Art Institute 
<P>Tianjin Conservatory of Music 
<P>Tianjin Institute of Physical Education 
<P>Tianjin Teachers' Training Academy 
<P>Tianjin Vocational College 
<P>Hebei University of Technological 
<P>
<HR>
<H3><STRONG>Some Famouse Middle Schools</STRONG> </H3>
<P>Yao Hua Middle School 
<P>Nankai Middle School 
<P>Tianjin No. 1 Middle School 
<P>Tianjin Experiemental Middle School 
<P>Tianjin Xinhua Middle School 
<P>
