<Title> Key Laboratories of Tianjin University</Title>
  
Tianjin University is equipped with advanced instruments and equipment for 
teaching and scientific work. Among the 84 laboratories, there are five key
laboraries, and three modern and large-scale central laboraries.<P>


<OL><B>1. National Engine Combustion Laboratory. <P>
2. National Chemical Engineering Laboratory. <P>
3. Computer Centre Laboratory. <P>
4. Analysis Centre Laboratory. <P>
5. Precision Instrument Centre Laboratory. <P>
etc.<P></B></OL>

The floor space of all laboratories totals 42,000 square metre with an 
experimental staff of 480,  15% of them being senior experimenters and engineers.<P>
</DOC>
