<TITLE> Research Institutes/Developmend of Tian Jin University</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>There are 14 Research Institute or Center in Tianjin University as list below:</H2>
<P>1. Tianjin Internal Combustion Engine Reserch Institute <BR>
2. Thermal Energy Institute <BR>
3. Chemical Engineering Research Institute <BR>
4. Institue of Modern Optical Instruments <BR>
5. Institute of Systems Engineering <BR>
6. Research Institute of Higher Education <BR>
7. Research Institute of Architectural Design <BR>
8. Computer Centre <BR>
9. Analysis Centre <BR>
10. Precision Instrumentation Centre <BR>
11. Tianjin R&amp;D centre for Petrochemical Technology <BR>
12. Tianjin Geothermal Research and Training Centre<BR>
