<TITLE>Department of Applied Chemistry</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Applied Chemistry</H3>
<HR><UL>There are three specialities for undergraduates:<BR>
<OL><I>Polymer Materials and its Application,<BR>Fine Chemical Engineering <BR>Applied Chemistry.</I></OL><P>The major research are :<I><OL>Dyestuff, Pigment, Auxiliary and Organic Intermediate, Electrodeposition of Metals, Organic-electrosynthesis, Conducting Polymer and Chemical Power Source, </I>which are developing towards <I>the frontier science of photoelectrochemistry, Bioelectrochemistry and Bio-Chemical Engineering.</OL></I></UL><BR><HR><P>






</DOC>
