<TITLE>Department of Architecture</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Architecture</H3>
<HR><UL>The Department has a long history, which was founded in Tianjin University in 1952. Now it has two specialties:  <BR><OL>Architectural Design and City Planning.</OL><BR>
In the recent three years, more than 33 of students won prizes in national student design competitions, and this well known in China. The department has close linkage with foreign countries.<BR>
Apart from the teaching work, the faculty and students have been engaged in professional training of city planners and Architects, and its graduates have been working in Building Design Institutes and City Planning Bureau throughout the country.</UL><HR><P>





</DOC>
