<TITLE>Department of Chemical Engineering</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Chemical Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>This Department at Tianjin University was reorganized in 1952 by combination of 7 Chemical Engineering Departments from different University: <I><OL>Peiyang, Nankai, Qinghua,etc.</OL></I> and is the largest department in term of the number of academic staff and students registered for undergraduate and postgraduate degrees. <BR>There are two national-rank key disciplines, i.e. <I>Cheical Engineering Science and Organic Chemical Technology</I>, 
and one National Laboratory.<P>
The department has seven research sections, for example, Reaction Engineering Chemical Process System Engineering, in which the Chemical Engineering institute of Tianjin University is established. </UL>
<BR><HR><P>






</DOC>
