<TITLE>Department of Chemistry</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Chemistry</H3>
<HR><UL><P>
The main scientific research directions of the department are :<I><OL>the exploitation and research of natural high polymer materials,<BR>the research of mechanism on Surface processes and the synthesis of surfactants, <BR>the research on chemical thermodynamics, <BR>the synthesis and analysis of fine chemicals.</OL></I></UL><P><HR>







