<TITLE>Department of Civil Engineering</TITLE>
<H3>  The Department of Civil Engineering  </H3>
<HR><UL>The Department of Civil Engineering is one of the oldest department in Tianjin University. <P>
The Department offers several academic programs, such as:<BR> <OL><I>Structural Engineering <BR>
Building Economics <BR>
Construction Management <BR>
Water Treatment and Water Resource Engineering <BR>
Computer Application in Engineering<BR>
Heat Engineering and Ventilation and Air Purification  Engineering </I></OL></UL><P><HR>


