<TITLE>Department of Computer Engineering and Science</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Computer Engineering and Science</H3>
<HR><UL>The computer science speciality established in the early 1960s as one of subjects <BR>in the university. In 1983, this department was founded.<P>
The major research directions are :<BR><I><OL>the fault tolerant computig <BR>
Microcomputer and its application <BR>
Multi-computer system and network <BR>
Artificial intelligence and CAE <BR>
Computer model recognization and image processing<BR>
Knowledge engineering and the technique of CAD/CAM<BR>
Computer controlling and software engineering.</OL></I></UL><P><HR>







