<Title> Department of Electronic Engineering </Title>
<H3>The Department of Electronic Engineering</H3>
<HR>The Department has an aboundant faculty. <BR>The divisions for undergraduate students in the department train and develop senior engineering in the following fields :<BR><I><OL>
design and manufacture of electronic systems and equipment;<BR>
design and manufacture of electronic instruments;<BR>
intelligent instruments and automatic test systems;<BR>
theoretical study and design of transistor and IC;<BR>
design and manufacture of semiconductor devices;<BR>
electronic materials and componants devices;<BR>
and microelectronic systems.
</OL></I> 
<P>The main research directions are :<BR><OL><I>
Speech and image procedding and transmission, electronic circuits, system CAD optimization design, <BR>
intelligent instrument and systems design, <BR>
electronic components and function materials, <BR>
New semiconducter Devices.
</I></OL><HR>
</DOC>
