<Title> Department of Electrical Engineering and Automation </Title>
<H3>The Department of Electrical Engineering and Automation</H3>
<UL>
The Department has a long history with 
strict training, aboundant academic staff and good educational condition.<P> The major subjects or fields in this department are :<BR><OL><I>
Automatic Control of Electrical Drives,<BR>
Electrification and Automation of Production Process,<BR>
Automatic Instruments and Process Control, <BR>
Power Plant and Power System,<BR>
Theory of Large Power Generating Equipment, <BR>
Medium and Small Micro and Special Electrical Machines,<BR>
Theory of General electrical Machines. <P></I></OL>
The purpose is to train senior engineering and technical personnel in theoretical study, design and control.
</UL>
<HR>


