<TITLE>Department of Foreign Languages</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Foreign Languages</H3>
<HR><UL>The Department undertakes two major teaching tasks:
<OL>teaching of foreign languages ( English, Japanese, Russian, and German ) to all students ( non-English majors )
of the University, and <BR>teaching of English for Science and Technology ( English major ).
</OL>The objective of EST program is to train the students to become intellectually and politically qualified EST workers, who have practical abilities of oral and written presentation and the relevant knowledge of science and technology, industry, and foreign trade. 
</UL><HR><P>






</DOC>
