<TITLE>Department of Humanities and Social Sciences</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Humanities and Social Sciences</H3>
<HR><UL>Its main orientation of scientific research is <OL>education on the Marxist theory, <BR>and historiography, <BR>philosophy, <BR>economics, <BR>Linguistics and literature.</OL> The department has capable teachers, who are engaged in teaching and scientific research. Many papers are published in recent years. The department offers courses which has basic theory and overall knowledge, so that students can be geared to the needs of social and practical work, and possess essential knowledge and capability.
</UL><HR><P>






