<TITLE>Department of Management Engineering</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Management Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>This Department was set in 1979, which is developing quickly and very 
active in academic field. It keeps close contract with foreign universities 
and research institutes. <BR>The graduates from the department are qualified to
 make decisions and to engage in systematic management at industial manadement
 engineering and capital construction management engineeing.<HR><P>






