<TITLE>Department of Material Science and Engineering</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Material Science and Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>The Department has worked on a number of important research projects on advanced materials and has gained great achievements. <P>
The major research direction are :<I><OL>heat treatment of metal;<BR>inorganic non-metal material manufacture and development;<BR>macromolecular material production and modification;<BR> and material corrosion and protection,etc. </OL></I></UL><P><HR>







