<TITLE>Department of Mathematics</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Mathematics</H3>
<HR><UL>This Department has trained strictly, emphasized to improve the quality of educaion, undertaken the teaching task of mathematical coures for undergraduate students and graduate students in this university.<P>
The major research fields are :<I><OL>applied statistics,<BR>
differential equations with application theory and application of optimization, <BR>functional analysis <BR>and so on.</OL></I></UL><HR><P>






