<Title>Department of Mechanical Engineering</Title>

<H3>The Department of Mechanical Engineering</H3><HR><UL>This Department is one of the oldest department of the University. It has advanced equipment as well as qualified and experienced 
faculty.  There are many valuable facilities, such as the modern machining center,
NC machine tools, laser instruments etc.. .<P>
The main research fields of this department are: 
	<OL><I>modern manufacturing system and techniques;<BR> 
	CAD/CAM/CAE, FMS, CIMS;<BR>
	mechanical dynamical design and test;<BR>
	special materials working robotics;<BR>
	intelligent machine;<BR>
	mechanology;<BR>
	noise control;<BR>
	Dies CAD/CAM;<BR>
	welding constructon, technology, electric source and arc;<BR>
	etc.</I></OL></UL><P><HR>
	



</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT27-B27-238</DOCNO>
