<TITLE>Department of Industrial Economics and Systems Engineering</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Industrial Economics and Systems Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>The Department has developed a number of specializaton areas among Economics, System Engineering and Management Information System. Among them, <B>System Engineering</B> is one of the national priority as a speciality.<BR>
The objectives of the department is training high grade Engineering-Management personnel who can master economical, secientific management theories and essential know how in their technical field therefore they can undertake the work such as <I>Project Economical Analysis and Population, Project Cost Management, Information system and the ability to partocopate in planning and designing work.</I></UL><HR><P>


