<TITLE>Department of Ocean Engineering and Naval Architecture </TITLE>
<H3>  The Department of Ocean Engineering and Naval Architecture </H3>
<HR><UL>The Department consists of  2 specialties: <BR>
<OL>Offshore Civil Engineering (being the first one in China when it was founded in Tianjin University in 1971);<BR>Naval Architecture.</OL><P>The main topics of research include :<BR><OL><I>
Characteristics of Ocean Environmental Consitions and Loads and Their interaction with Offshore Structures or ships;<BR>
Reliability Analysis of Ocean Engineering Conditios nad Optimum design of Offshore, Structure or Ships. <BR>
</I></OL></UL><P><HR>




