<TITLE>Department of Physics</TITLE>
<H3>The Department of Physics</H3>
<HR><UL>The predecessor of the Physics Department was the Physics Department of Peiyang University, which was established in 1946. The Department was reestablished in 1979. <P>
The research fields of this Department are :<I><OL>
Condense-State Physics,<BR> Modern Optics,<BR>Biophysics,<BR> Theoretical Physics,<BR> Computing Physics,<BR> etc.</OL></I></UL><P><HR>







