<Title> Department of Precision Instruments Engineering </Title>
<H3>The Department of Precision Instruments Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>The Department of Precision Instruments Engineering was found in 1952. There is faculty with profound background of special knowlodge, advanced equipment, and all kinds of books and magazines on its specialities.<P>
It is famous for its vigerous studied and scientific researches.
It has gained praises not only from China but also from foreign countried on tremendous achievements for many times.<P>
Its main task is to bring up students to high-level being able to master scientific research and instrument manufacture in <OL><I>precision test and instruments, <BR>photo--electronic precision machine and instruments,<BR>timing instruments, <BR>new type analytic instruments, <BR>laser technique application, <BR>and modern bio-medical instruments respectively.</I></OL></UL><P><HR>


