<Title> Department of Thermophysics Engineering </Title>
<H3>The Department of Thermophysics Engineering</H3>
<HR><UL>
The Department has vety favourable conditions, in which the national key discipline, the natonal-rank key laboratory and the postdoctoral station have been set up. The academic leader in the research field of 
internal combustion engine, Professor Shi Shao-xi is a member of the Chinese 
Academy of Science.<P> The students of this department are qualified for the jobs
in the following fields: <OL><I>
Internal Combustion Engine and its relative trades, <BR>the utilization of thermal energy and the energy-saving techniques, <BR>the design 
and investigation of heat-exchanging equipment.</I></OL></UL><P><HR>

