<TITLE>NATIONAL ENGINEERING RESEARCH CENTRE OF DIE & MOLD CAD </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>NATIONAL ENGINEERING RESEARCH CENTRE OF DIE &amp; MOLD CAD </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Shanghai Jiaotong University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of ERC: <B>Prof. Ruan Xueyu </B></H3>
<HR>
<H3>Major Researchers:<BR>
 </H3>
<P><B>Prof. Zhang Yongqing</B><BR>
 <B>Prof. Zhang Zhiliang</B><BR>
 <B>Prof. Zhou Chixing</B><BR>
 
<HR>
<P><B>Director of ERC: Prof. Ruan Xueyu </B><BR>
 <BR>
 Ruan Xueyu, academician of the Engineering Academy of China, the director, professor and Ph.D. supervisor of the Dept. plasticity technology in Shanghai Jiaotong Univ. was born in 1933. Prof. Ruan is director of Shanghai Research Institute of Tool &amp; Die Technology which is established by him in 1933. Prof. Ruan is also a famous expert in the Metal Forming and Die &amp; Mold fields. in 1985, he was titled as the National Distinguished Expert. He was also enrolled as the Famous Person of World five times. Up to now, he was written five books which contain 1200, 000 words, such as The Cold Extrusion Technology and so on. And Prof. Ruan has won the science and technology progress prize of state, province and ministry seven times. <BR>
 <BR>
 Tel: 021-2820841<BR>
 EMAIL:xyruan@situ. edu. cn <BR>
 <BR>
 <B>Director of academic committee of REC: Prof. Zuo Tieyong </B><BR>
 <BR>
 Zuo Tieyong, academician of the Engineering Academy of China, director of dept. of science and technology of state education commission P. -R. professor and Ph.D. supervisor of Dept. of materials science and engineering in Central South Univ. of Technology, was born in 1936. Prof. Zuo is also a famous expert in Materials Science And METAL Forming fields. From 1985 to 1991, Prof. Zuo has been vice president of central South Univ. of Technology. He as titled as the National Distinguished Expert in 1990. He has win the science and technology progress prizes of state, province and ministry eleven times. <BR>
 <BR>
 Tel: 010-69097062<BR>
 EMAIL: <BR>
 <BR>
 <B>Major Researcher: </B><BR>
 <B>Zhang Yongqing</B>, professor, vice director and Ph.D. supervisor of Dept. of plasticity technology in shanghai Jiaotong Univ. , vice director of Shanghai Research Institute of Tool &amp; die Technology, was born in 1939. Prof. Zhang is also member of Germany Tribology Society vice director of Shanghai Tribology Society. The major research directions are wear and lubrication of die &amp; mold materials. Up to now, he has published 22 papers. <BR>
 <B>Zhang Zhiliang</B>, professor ad Ph.D. supervisor of Dept. of plasticity Technology in Shanghai Jiaotong Univ. , was born in 1934. the major research directions are die &amp; mold of cold extrusion and its CAD. Prof. Zhang has written two books and published 20 papers. <BR>
 <B>Huang Riqing</B>, professor of Shanghai Jiaotong Univ. , Vice director of national engineering CAD training networks committee, was born in 1943. The major research direction is the CAD/CAPP/CAM of die &amp; mold. Prof. Huang has presided the CIMS application object-CAD/CAM system design which belongs to national high technology plan in designing of the Secon Textile machinery factory. Prof. Huang has won the science and Technology progress prize if state education com-mission two times. He has written five books and published more than 20 papers.<BR>
 <B>Peng Yinghong</B>, Ph.D., associate professor and vice director of the Dept. of plasticity technology in Shanghai Jiaotong Univ. , Director of CAD research division of Shanghai Research Institute of Tool &amp; Die Technology, the member of the New York Academy of Sciences, was born in 1963. The major research direction is the numerical simulation of plastic forming process. He has published 26 papers. <BR>
 <B>Zhang Weigang</B>, Ph.D. , associate professor and vice director of the Dept. of plasticity technology in the Shanghai Jiaotong Univ. , was born in 1963. The major research directions are 3D numerical simulation of metal forming process and rolling theory. 
<HR>
<H3>Objectives: </H3>
<P>By laying special emphasis on plastic dies and stamping dies and attacking CAM as a breach to break through, improve the PC CAD/CAM system of stamping dies, perfect the workstation CAD/CAM/CAE system of plastic dies, and develop the CAD/CAM/CAE system. 
<HR>
