 EDM (FS-A3C; 95,5 ) 
<HR>
<H3>The Introduction of the Major Research Directions of ERC</H3>
<P><B>The major research directions of ERC covers four fields such as follows: </B><BR>
 <B>1)Die &amp; Mould CAD/CAM </B><BR>
 So far, the software developed by ERC such as Stamping Die &amp; Mold CAD/CAM Injection Mold CAD/CAM, Extrusion Die CAD, Drawing Die CAD and Continuous Blanking Die CAD/CAM have been used by over 2000 users all over the country and met the requests from most factories. At the same time, ERC also has developed and adsorbed various types of the graphic support software systems for Die CAD/CAM. So it provides the strong methods to describe the graphic for the further research work in the [plastic-deform theory. The ERC's research work in some fields has been counted among the best either in China or over the world. These fields includes the engineering data base special for Die &amp; Mold CAD/CAM. The expert system for Die &amp; Mold Design, the CNC wire-cut technology for super-thickness part.<BR>
 <B>2)The Numerical Simulation of the Metal Forming Processes </B><BR>
 At the begin of 1980's, ERC has already done some research work in the numerical simulation of the metal forming Process. It was the first one in China. Up to now, based on the plastic mechanics, the fluid mechanics. the plastic deform technology and the computer graphics, a general purpose simulation software system-S-FORM has been developed by ERC. This software is focus on solving the large deformation, non-liner plastic flow Problem and it is the most advance among the software just this kind in China. At the same time, in this research field, seven high-level dissertations for doctor degree have been finished and they are highly appraised by the experts.<BR>
 <B>3)The AI Research In the Plastic-forming Processes </B><BR>
 At the end of 1980's, ERC had carried out the research works in the application of AI(Artificial Intelligent) to analyze the plastic forming processes at first time in China. So far, the Injection-Mold AI System which has been finished by ERC has been appraised highly by the experts of China and other countries. At the some time, AI-Numerical System and AI-Stamping-Die &amp; Mold CAD System are under-developing in ERC. <BR>
 <B>4)The Physics Simulation and Optimization of the Plastic forming Process</B><BR>
 ERC has finished eight research Projects issued by the state, the State ministry, commission and Shanghai government in the fields of cold and warm extrusion, pressure rolling and the friction problem during the plastic deformation processes and so on and these projects were conferred respectively the awards of state, province, ministry, commission and Shanghai government. Now, ERC is doing some researches on the technology parameter optimization of plastic forming process and physics simulation. 
<HR>
