<TITLE>NATIONAL ENGINEERING RESEARCH CENTRE OF TURBO-GENERATOR VIBRATION </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>NATIONAL ENGINEERING RESEARCH CENTRE OF TURBO-GENERATOR VIBRATION </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>South East University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of ERC: <B>Prof. Gao Wei </B></H3>
<HR>
<P>Objectives: 
<P>To counter large turbo-generators in China, the ERC will research &amp; develop the advanced rotor-bearing system vibration design technology, off-line and on-line vibration measurement, diagnosis and trouble shoot- ing method. Meanwhile, the ERC will develop and product with small-scale the high performance vibration condition monitoring, analysis and diagnostics equipment and systems for turbo machinary. 
<HR>
<P>Major Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Lu Songyuan</B><BR>
 <B>Prof. Wang Yu sheng</B><BR>
 <B>Assoc. Prof. Zhang Zhufan</B><BR>
 
