<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Xi'an Jiaotong University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of ERC: <B>Prof. Shu Pengcheng </B></H3>
<HR>
<P>Objectives: 
<P>Takes large and medium compressors in major installations and numerous widespread new-type compressors, fans and pumps as its objects of development and research. Works out key techniques so as to provide enterprises with overall research achievements which will satisfy market demand. 
