<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SURFACE PHYSICS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SURFACE PHYSICS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Fudan University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wang Xun </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Xie Xide </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Si molecular beam epitaxy, Silicon-Germenium heterostructures, quantum wells, superlattices and silicon band gap engineering. 
<LI>Investigation on the surfaces and interfaces of III-V compound semiconductors (atomic and electronic structures of clean surfaces, hetero-interfaces of III-V/III-V and IV/III-V systems, metal-semiconductor interfaces, passivation of semiconductor surfaces). 
<LI>Development of new surface analytical techniques (surface emptystate spectroscopy and scanning tunneling microscopy.) 
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab of Surface Physics, Fudan University, Shanghai 200433, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-21-5492222 Ext 2683<BR>
 (86)-21-5490593<BR>
 
<LI>Cable:33317 HUAFU CN<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-21-3269848<BR>
 
</UL>
