</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF OCEAN ENGINEERING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Shanghai Jiao Tong University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Sheng Zhenbang </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Qiu Dahong </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The analysis of the hydrodynamic loads on ship and offshore structures and their motions under the influence of the environment conditions (such as wind, wave and currents); the simulations and analysis of the technical problems appeared during the processes of building, launching and installing of ships and offshore structures; the simulation and performance analysis of harbors, wharf and the vibration of piles and rises; basic investigations on offshore structures of new type. 
