</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF VIBRATION SHOCK AND NOISE </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Shanghai Jiaotong University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Han Zushun </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Wen Bangchun </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The emphasis is on the mechanism of vibration, shock and noise control for machinery and dynamic characteristics for power mechanical structures. New ways to isolate vibration, to absorb shock and to reduce noise level. To look into experimental techniques, signal processing and new material. Endeavor to raise the safety characteristics and improve acousticsurroundings of machinery equipments. 
<HR>
