<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>East China Normal University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Mei Anxin </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Liu Shuren </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Urban Remote Sensing, urbanization monitoring, urban planning, urban disaster, image processing, cartography, techniques and approaches of remote sensing. 
<LI>Environmental Arvhaeological Remote sensing: archaeilogical survey and cartography, detection of underground relics, advance techniques for achaeological survey. 
<LI>Geographic information system. 
<LI>
</OL>
<HR>
