<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF BIOREACTORS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF BIOREACTORS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>East China University of Science and Technology 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Yu Juntang </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Guo Musun </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Research and development of new dioreactors for microbial fermentation, animal and plant cell cultivatio or enzymatic reaction to meet the requirements of production of new biotechnological products. 
<LI>Improvement of the performance of existed bioreactors in biotechnological factories, including to improve the controlling systems for bioprocess optimization. 
<LI>Carrying out some basic studies on hydrodynamic, mixing and mass, transfer for characteristics in bioreactors, methods for bioreator scale-up and bioprocess optimization. 
</OL>
<HR>
