<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF ADVANCED WELDING PRODUCTION TECHNOLOGY </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF ADVANCED WELDING PRODUCTION TECHNOLOGY </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Harbin Institute of Engineering 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wang Qilong </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Guan Qiao </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Stress, distortion and reliability of welded construction, nondestructive testing. 
<LI>Arc and plasma welfing process, arc welding process, arc welding power supplies and automatic welding equipment. 
<LI>Welding and joining technology of materials. 
<LI>Robotic welding and intelligence control of welding processes. 
<LI>Laser processing technology and its control system. 
<LI>Special welding processes and pressure welding technology. 
</OL>
<HR>
