 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Tang Auchin </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>To investigate chemical bonds of new organic and in organic molecules, polymers and solid state materials and to develop molecular design and material design. 
<LI>To explore new energy source matter and to investigate their structures and propertiers. 
<LI>To investigate chemical problems in biology. 
<LI>To investigate basic theory in quantum chemistry and to develop new computational techniques. 
</OL>
