<TITLE>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF INORGANIC HYDROTHERMAL SYNTHESIS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF INORGANIC HYDROTHERMAL SYNTHESIS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Jilin University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Xu Ruren </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Chen Jiayong </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The hydrothermal synthesis of new and functional inorganic Compounds, reaction mechanism, and relationship between properties and structures. Research are emphasized on the preparation of complex oxides, coordination compounds, clusters, special condensed solids and new microporous crystals under hydrothermal conditions with high-temperature and high-pressure. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Feng Shouhua</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Qiu Shilun</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Li Shougui</B><BR>
