<TITLE>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF MOLECULAR SPECTRA AND STRUCTURE </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF MOLECULAR SPECTRA AND STRUCTURE </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Jilin University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Shen Jiacong </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Zhang Cunhao </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Vibration-Rotation spectroscopy of small molecular system and their theory analysis; Structure of complex molecular; Structure of complex molecular; Structure of supermolecular system such as organic thin films: bionic membrance, multipeptide assemble; Dynamic spectra of transmission process of energy, electron and information in supermolecular system. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Zhang Xi</B><BR>
<B> Assoc.Prof. Zhao Bing</B><BR>
<B> Assoc.Prof. Ma Yuguang</B><BR>
<B> </B>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>The Research Lab of SEDC of Molecular Spectra and Structure, Jilin University, Changchun 130023, Jinlin, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-431-8923189 Ext.2878<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-431-8923907<BR>
 
</UL>
