<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF ROLLING TECHNOLOGY AND AUTOMATION OF TANDON ROLLING </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF ROLLING TECHNOLOGY AND AUTOMATION OF TANDON ROLLING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Northeast University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Du Songshan </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Bai Guangrun </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Its main orientation is directed to the research and development of new tandom rolling processes, drivers and control techniques and computer system of automation to implement new tandom rolling technology and realize optimal control and advanced automation of the tandom rollong process. The general target os to achieve energy and material saving and improvement of product quality. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Liu Xianghua</B><BR>
 <B>Accoc.Prof. Wu Di</B><BR>
