</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF COASTAL AND OFFSHORE ENGINEERING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Dalian University of Technology 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wang Yongxue </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Qiu Dahong </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Waves, currents and other hydrodynamic factors and the interaction between these factors and structures; the interaction between the hydrodynamic factors and two phases flow problems; the structural analysis, design and material research of the coastal and offshore engineering structures; the seismic resistant research of coastal and offshore engineering structures. 
