<BODY>
<H2>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF COMPREHENSIVE UTILIZATION FOR CARBON RESOURCES </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Dalian University of Science and Technology 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wang Xiangsheng </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Lin Liwu </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Based upon the carbon resources, mainly from coal and their derivatives, including: 
<OL>
<LI>Coal structure and coal conversion techniques. 
<LI>Hydrocarbon conversion and utilization techniques. 
<LI>CO chemistry and their fine chemicals development. 
<LI>Plasma activated techniques for utilization of carbon resources. 
<LI>Relavent techniques and methods in analysis and characterization research. 
</OL>
<HR>
