<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MULTIPHASE FLOW IN POWER ENGINEERING </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MULTIPHASE FLOW IN POWER ENGINEERING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Xi`an Jiaotong University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Chen Xuejun </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Chen Xuejun </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Investigation on gas-liquid(vapor-liquid) two-phase flow and heat and mass transfer; investigation on wet steam two-phase flow in turbine machinery; investigation on oil-gas-water three-phase flow and its heat and mass transfer; investigation on cryogenic two-phase flow and its heat and mass transfer; investigation on gas-solid two-phase flow and its heat and mass transfer; investigation on liquid-liquid and liquid-solid two-phase flow; investigation on teo-phase heat transfer enhancement. 
<HR>
<P>Photo: 
<P><A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_1.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_1.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_2.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_2.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_3.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_3.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_4.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A037/a37_4.icojpg " ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> 
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab of Multiphase Flow in Power Engineering, Xi`an Jiaotong University, Xi`an 710049, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-29-335011 Ext 3947<BR>
 
<LI>Cable:Xi`an 2827<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-29-337910<BR>
 
