<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MECHAMICAL BEHAVIOR OF METALLIC MATERIALS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MECHAMICAL BEHAVIOR OF METALLIC MATERIALS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Xi'an Jiaotong University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. He Jiawen </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Zhou Lian </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Evaluation and criteria of metallic materials for fracture and fatigue resistance in various environments and at various loading rates, the macro properties are assocoated with micro structure. Mechanical properties of surface modified by implantation and/or diffusion. Processes for non-ferrous metals, metal matrix composites and advanced organic and polymeric materials their mechanical properties. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Xu Kewei</B><BR>
 <B>Prof. Zheng Maosheng</B><BR>
 <B>Assoc.Prof. Song Xiaoping</B><BR>
 
