<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF FERMENTATION TECHNOLOGY </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Shandong University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Qian Xinmin </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Yu Juntang </B></H3>
