<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Southeast University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Gu Guangqun </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Wang Nengbin </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Computer network and open distributed processing. 
<LI>Database and information system. 
<LI>Supporting techniques for information integration. 
</OL>
<HR>
