<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF CAD &CG </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF CAD &amp;CG </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Shi Jiaoying </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Liang Youdong </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Computer Aided Design and Computer Graphics which including CAD support software, engineering database, mechanical product CAD, electrical CAD, architecture CAD, arts and crafts CAD, algorithms and theories of graphics, graphics software and hardware, virtual reality, scientific data visualization, graphical input and interaction, dynamic display and simulation. 
