<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SILICON MATERIALS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SILICON MATERIALS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Senior Engineer Yao Hongnian </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Lin Lanying </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The study of high-purity near intrinsic single crystal silicon; CZ single crystal silicon containing trace amount of nitrogen, including: basic theory, micro-structure; growth mechanism and Si-N reaction dynamics, electrical and mechanical behaviors; characteristics of single crystal silicon containing trace amount of nitrogen for IC uses; basic theoretical research of granular polycrystal silicon; epitaxial growth of silicon with silane; the study of surface and interface of silicon material. 
<HR>
<P><A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_1.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_1.icojpg " ALIGN="TOP"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_2.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_2.icojpg " ALIGN="TOP"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_3.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_3.icojpg " ALIGN="TOP"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_4.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A030/a30_4.icojpg " ALIGN="TOP"></A> 
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab of High Purity Silicon, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 310027, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-571-572244 Ext 2851<BR>
 
<LI>Tele:35040 ZUFAO CN<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-571-571792<BR>
 
</UL>
<P>
