<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MODERN OPTICAL INSTRUMENTS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MODERN OPTICAL INSTRUMENTS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Tang Jinfa </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Mu Guoguang </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Optics, mechanics and computer integrated detecting instruments. 
<LI>Optical technology of thin film. 
<LI>Radiation measurement technics and physiological optics studies. 
<LI>Laser and non-linear optics. 
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Chen Jun</B><BR>
