<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF FLUID POWER TRANSMISSION AND CONTROL </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF FLUID POWER TRANSMISSION AND CONTROL </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wu Genmao </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Lu Yongxiang </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The laboratory is mainly devoted to the theorotical and experimental research, applying engineering control theory, microelectronic technology and iol hydraulics theory and using inner feedback and PWM, PDM techmology, on the basic principles, control strategics and engineering application of large/medium electrodraulic and electropneumatic/serv control devices and systems with high performence, low cost and solid reliavity. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Yang Huayong</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Chen Ying</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Fu Zhoudong</B><BR>
<B> </B>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab. of Fluid Power Transmission and control, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 310027, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-571-5123314<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-571-7951358<BR>
 
</UL>
