<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF INDUSTRIAL PROCESS CONTROL </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF INDUSTRIAL PROCESS CONTROL </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Wang Shuqing </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Sun Youxian </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The Primary goal of NLICT is focused on the research of applied fundamental theory of complicated industrial process automatic control technology, including robust control, adaptive control, fault-tolerant control, intelligent control, system modeling and simulation, failure diagnosis, production-scheduling, computer and network techniques for industrial control, advanced measurement technology and sophisticated instruments. 
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Wu Tiejun</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Li Ping</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Chu jian</B><BR>
<B> </B>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab. of Industrial Process Control, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 310027, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-571-7951358<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-571-5122107<BR>
 
</UL>
