<TITLE>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF CLEAN COMBUSTION TECHNOLOGY </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF CLEAN COMBUSTION TECHNOLOGY </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Zhejiang University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Yan Jianhua </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Cen Kefa </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Combustion technology of new oil-substituting coal siurry. 
<LI>Fluidized-bed combined generation of biomass and coal vapor-gas. 
<LI>Heat/power combined generation of biomass and coal vapor-gas. 
<LI>Generation of solid or fluid/solid waste and toxic organic waste water. 
<LI>Low-polluting intensified combustion technology of power station boller. 
<LI>The theoretical study of multi-phase flow and computer-aided numerical testing. 
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Fan Jianren</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Yan Jianhua</B><BR>
<B> Prof. Luo Zhongyang</B><BR>
<B> </B>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>The research Laboratory of SEDC of Clean-Combustion Technology, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 310027, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-571-5126616<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-571-7951358<BR>
 
</UL>
