<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF PHYSICAL CHEMISTRY OF THE SOLID SURFACE </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF PHYSICAL CHEMISTRY OF THE SOLID SURFACE </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Xiamen University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Tian Zhaowu </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Cai Qirui </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The study of the systems of heterogeneous catalysis, electrochemical interfaces and membrane materials; investigating the composition and structure of the surface as well as the kinetics and mechanisms of the adsorption and chemical process; establishing quantum chemical methods and characterization techniques for above system at molecular level; developing theories of heterogeneous catalysis and electrode kinetics. 
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab of Physical chemistry of the solid surface, Xiamen University, Fujian 361005, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-592-227400<BR>
 (86)-592-227405<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-592-227496<BR>
 
</UL>
