<TITLE>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF TUMOR CELL ENGINEERING </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>THE RESEARCH LABORATORY OF SEDC OF TUMOR CELL ENGINEERING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Xianmen University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Su Wenjin </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Zhai Zhonghe </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>The study of the action of biochemical factors for induction of the differentiation of neoplastic cells and the mechanisms of their differentiation. 
<LI>The analytic studies of gene regulation of tumor cells and of the effects of anti-sense RNAs on growing cancer cells. 
<LI>Searching for killing or hindering factors against cancer cells by immunological study. 
<LI>
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Dr. Su Wenjin</B><BR>
<B> Dr. Wen Longping</B><BR>
<B> Dr. Li Qifu</B><BR>
<B> </B>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>The Research Laboratory of SEDC of Tumor Cell Engineering, Xiamen University, Xiamen 381005, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-592-2085103 Ext.5301<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-592-2086496<BR>
 
</UL>
