<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF COMPUTER SOFTWARE ENGINEERING </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF COMPUTER SOFTWARE ENGINEERING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Wuhan University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. He Keqing </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Chen Huowang </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Software development environments; essential theory on software engineering; software engineering environment supporting non-numerical parallel algorithms; software reliability evaluation; knowledge-based software development environments; implementation of application software systems which sets an engineering example, and graphics processing. 
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
