<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY ON COAL COMBUSTION </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY ON COAL COMBUSTION </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Huazhong University of Science and Technology 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Zheng Chuguang </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The theory and technology of coal combustion for high efficiency, low pollution and low cost. Including mechanism of reaction kinetics and aerodynamics of coal combustion; heat and mass transfer mechanism during combustion process; formation of pollutants and its control; mathematical physical model of combustion process and its numeral simulation; diagnosis and optimization of coal combustion process; development of new combustion technology. 
<HR>
<P>Photo: 
<P><A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_1.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_1.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_2.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_2.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> <A HREF="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_3.jpg"><IMG SRC="/cnkeylab/STATE/A036/a36_3.icojpg" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A> 
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab on Coal Combustion, Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Wuhan Hubei, 430074, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-27-701152<BR>
 
<LI>Cable:7122<BR>
 
<LI>Telex:40121 HBHUT CN<BR>
 
