<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY IN GENETIC IMPROVEMENTS OF CROPS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Huazhong Agricultural University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Xie Yuefeng </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Liu Houli </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>Studies on theories, techniques and approaches in crop genetic improvements at population, individual, cell and molecular level, including: genetics of crop quality, yields and stress tolerance; genetic basis and mechanisms of hybrid vigor; creation, development and utilization of new germplasms; molecular genetics, genome mapping and gene transfer of crop plants. 
