<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MEDICAL GENETICS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF MEDICAL GENETICS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Hunan Medical University 
</UL>
<P></U>
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Li Luyun </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Xia jiahui </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<P>The basic and application study or Medical Genetics. Using the modern cytogenetic, molecular cytgenetic and molecular genetic techniques, we study inherited basis and mechanism responsible for some genetic diseases, which result in malformation, mental retardation and disability. Finally, to reach the goal of diagnosis prevention and cure of some common genetic diseases. 
