<TITLE> Chairman of academic Committee </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF FUNCTIONAL POLYMER MATERIALS FOR ADSORPTION AND SEPARATION </H2>
<HR>
<P>
<H2>Chairman of academic Committee</H2>
<HR>
<H3></H3>
<H3>He Binglin</H3>
<P>Academician of Chinese Academy of Science and a Supervisor of Ph. D.  
candidate.  He is one of pioneers in the field of polymer chemistry in china. 
 His outstanding contribution to several fields of polymer science such as 
functional polymeric materials has made him win great prestige.  He has got 
13 prizes including national natural science,   national innovation and 
advancement of science and technology of ministries and commissions or 
municipal committee.  He has co-authored 5 patents,   written chapters in 1 
monograph and published more than 400 scientific papers.  Under the 
leadership of Prof.  He Binglin,   a research group with suitable age 
structure,   rational academic echelon and active academic idea is formed. 
<HR>
<P><B>Phone:</B> 022-3501386 
<HR>
<P><B>Fax:</B> 022-3504853 
<HR>
<P>
<ADDRESS><B>Email:</B> <A HREF="mailto:sorp@linux.nankan.edu.cn ">sorp@linux.nankan.edu.cn </A></ADDRESS>
</BODY>
