	<H2>
	STATE KEY LABORATORY OF POLYMER MATERIALS ENGINEERING</H2><P>
	
        
	<PRE><H2>Open Subjects of the Laboratory</H2><PRE><P>
              
<HR>

<UL><PRE><H3>
. High Li Ionic Migrating Solid Electrolyte
. Chemrhological Properties of Ether Ketone Epoxy and Processing of
  Carbon Fiber Reinforced Composites
. The Structure and Properties of New Polymeric Micro composites
. Cellulose Derivatives Composite having Cholephase Structure
. Theoretical Study and CAE of Dynamic Process of Polymer Reactive
  Blending
. Graft & Block Polymers and Their Surface Properties
. Irradiation Cross link of LDPE/LLDPE Blends
. The Interfacial Structure, Aging and Reaction Mechanism
. Preparation of Polyvinyl alcohol Bio-degraded Film and Study on the
  Decomposing Velocity
. The Friction and Wear of Viscoelastomers in Dynamic contact process
. Functional Mulch Films of Grass Fiber
. Polymer Alloys of Cavitation and Punching Wear Resistance
. Polymer Reactive Blending Systems
. Thermoplastic Molecular Composites
. The Effect of Hydrogen Bond on High Functional Semi-IPN
. Polyether ester-Inorganic Salt Composite
. New Technology of Ring-opening Polymer and Aldehyde Resin
. Polymer Composites Filled by Super fine

</H3></PRE></UL>

