<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF NEW CERAMICS AND FINE PROCESSING </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF CERAMICS AND FINE PROCESSING </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Tsinghua University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Li Lingtu </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Yao Xi </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Requiring new ceramics with mechanical properties of high temperature, high strengrh and high toughness, investigating their toughening mechanism and fractual mechanics. 
<LI>Study in adcanced ceramics with optimized properties of ferroelectrics, dielectrics, pie electrics, semi-conductuvuty, and conductiruty, microstructures and defect chemistry. 
<LI>Studying structures and properties of ceratmic based composites with whisker reinforced. 
<LI>Materials chemistry, bioceramics, materials bionics, microware synthesisand simtering, and other special preparation processing. 
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Major Young Researchers:<BR>
 
<P><B>Prof. Huang Yong</B><BR>
