<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SWITCHING TECHNOLOGY & TELECOMMUNICATION NETWORKS </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF SWITCHING TECHNOLOGY &amp; TELECOMMUNICATION NETWORKS </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Beijing University of Posts and Telecommunications 
