<TITLE>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF TURBULENCE RESEARCH </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>STATE KEY LABORATORY OF TURBULENCE RESEARCH </H2>
<P><U><B> </B>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>Peking University 
</UL>
<P></U> 
<H3>Director of Lab: <B>Prof. Shi Xungang </B><BR>
 Chairman of Academic Committee: <B>Prof. Zhuang Fengan </B></H3>
<P>
<HR>
<P>Main Research Fields: 
<OL>
<LI>Flow transition and stability. 
<LI>Statistical theory of shear turbulence. 
<LI>Coherent structures of shear turbulence. 
<LI>Turbulence modelling. 
<LI>Direct numerical simulation of turbulence. 
<LI>Vortex dynamic method of turbulence. 
<LI>Nonlinear dynamic route of turbulence, 
<LI>Lagrangian turbulence. 
<LI>Bifurcation and chaos of low dimensional dynamic system. 
<LI>Experimental research and measuremental technique of turbulence. 
</OL>
<HR>
<P>Address: 
<P>
<H4></H4>
<UL>
<LI>State Key Lab of Turbulence Research Department of Mechanics, Peking University, Beijing 100871, P.R.China <BR>
 
<LI>Tel:(86)-10-62501991<BR>
 
<LI>Fax:(86)-10-62501992<BR>
 
</UL>
<P>
</BODY>
