<Title> Time of Application </Title>
<h2>1.Undergraduates:</h2>
<h3>
<UL>Between March 1 and May 30 of each year.<BR>
Be enrolled in early September.</UL><HR></h3>
<h2>2. Candidates for a Master's degree:</h2> 
<h3><UL>
Between September 1 and the end of December of each year.<BR>
Be enrolled in early September.</UL></h3><HR>
<h2>3. Candidates for a Doctorate:</h2>
<h3><UL>Admission is conducted twice a year. 
Autumn admission procedures are as given for Candidates for Master's degree.
Spring admission procedures are as follows: applications can apply between February 1 
and the end of May, admission notices will be mailed out in September.
</UL></h3><HR>
<h2>4. Advanced Students and Chinese Language Program:</h2>
<h3><UL>Applications can apply any time.</UL></h3><HR>
