<Title>Curriculum Offered by the Chinese Language Centre</Title>
<h2>A. General Chinese (Elementary & Intermediate)</h2>
<h3>
<UL>1. Listening Comprehension<P>
2. Conversational Chinese<P>
3. Listening and Speaking<P>
4. Intensive Reading<P>
5. Look, Listen and Speak<P>
6. Chinese Vocabulary<P>
7. Practical Conversation<P>
8. Composition<P>
9. Spoken Chinese in Business<P>
10. Guide for Chinese Language Level Test(HSK)<P>
11. Chinese History<P>
12. Lecture on Chinese Culture<P>
13. Chinese Calligraphy<P>
14. Chinese Tourism Geography<P>
15. Selected Readings in Chinese Literary Works<P>
16. Chinese Arts Brief History<P>
17. Modern World and China<P>
18. Lecture of Art in Beijing Opera<P>
</UL><HR></h3>
<h2>B. Scientific Chinese</h2>
<h3>
<UL>1. Listening Comprehension<P>
2. Spoken Chinese<P>
3. Intensive Reading<P>
4. Composition<P>
5. Practical Conversation<P>
6. Technical Conversation<P>
7. Training for Looking and Listening<P>
8. Chinese History of Science and Technology<P>
9. Chinese Culture<P>
10. Spoken Chinese in Business<P>
11. Chinese Calligraphy<P>
12. Chinese Shadow Boxing<P>
</UL><HR></h3>
