<Title>Notes</Title>
<h3>The Self-supporting foreign students should have financial guarantor and 
enough money to pay all their fee and expenses for the whole academic year by 
U.S. dollars when they register.<P>
The above students must obey "The Regulations for Students Studying at Tianjin 
University" after they enter the school.

