<Title>Application Procedures and Formalities for Visa to China</Title>
Applicants or universities, colleges, organizations and other institutes of 
various are welcome to send organized groups of students to attend any of the 
above programs in Tianjin University. The applicants should submit the following documents:
<UL>1. <B>"Application Form for Foreigners Wishing to Study at Tianjin University 
in China"</B><BR>
2. A <B>"Physical Examination Record for Foreigners"(Photocopy)</B><BR>
3. 10 2*1 inch photos of the applicant (the photo should be half-length, full-face and
bare-headed) plus his/her passport number.<BR>
4. Duplicated copies of notarized diploma, degree, school-certified transcript 
of complete academic records and recommendation letters.
</DOC>
