<Title>Admission Qualifications for Candidates for a Doctorate</Title>
<h3>The applicant must have a Master's degree or be the equivalent of a Master's degree 
holder in China. He/She should submit his/her diploma, research plans and 
recommendation letters from two professors . He/She should be in good 
health and well behaved. Approved by the school, he/
she can apply for admission of doctoral program at Tianjin University.
Acceptance is decided by selection after a screening process. The lectures 
will be given in English  or in Chinese.<P>
   If the application is a graduate from a Chinese university and wishes to study for
 a doctoral degree at Tianjin University, he/she may be directly admitted with the
 recommendation from experts of his/her previous school and grades while 
studying in china along with knowledge of his/her scientific research capabilities.
</DOC>
<DOC>
