<Title>For Pre-studying Chinese Language Program</Title>
<h3>The undergraduate applicant approved by the school to study in Tianjin University and being 
incapable of studying his/her specialized courses in Chinese at the Chinese Language Center
for one year after admission to the university.
After passing the Chinese Language level test (HSK), he/she may apply for 
undergraduate courses. Other requirements are the same as mentioned above.
</DOC>
