<Title>List of Specialities for Undergraduates</Title>
<h2>List of Specialities for Undergraduates</h2>
<h3>
<UL>1. Technology and Equipment of Machining Process<P>
2. Photoelectronics Technique and Instruments<P>
3. Internal Combustion Engines<P>
4. Electrical Power Systems and their Automation<P>
5. Computer Applications<P>
6. Architecture<P>
7. Structural Engineering<P>
8. Hydraulic & Hybro-electric Engineering Construction<P>
9. Applied Mathematics<P>
10. Inorganic Non metallic Materials<P>
11. Chemical Engineering and Technology<P>
</UL>
</h3><HR>
</DOC>
