<Title>Admission Qualifications for Undergraduates</Title>
<h3>The applicant, who is at least the equivalent of a graduate of senior high 
school in China, capable of studying his.her specialized courses i Chinese, is 
well behaved, in good health and under the age of 25, can apply for admission 
of undergraduate  courses to Tianjin University. Acceptance is decided by 
selection after a screening process.
</DOC>
<DOC>
