<Title>For Senior Advanced Students</Title>
<h3>The applicant, who is at least the equivalent of a graduate of Master's 
degree in China , or has already obtain the qualification of studying for doctoral
 degree,can pursue his/her advanced studies on a certain subject under the 
direction of Chinese supervisors after admission to Tianjin University. He/She 
should be in good health and well behaved. Lectures can be given in English or in Chinese.

</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT27-B27-430</DOCNO>
