<Title>For General Advanced Students</Title>
<h3>The applicant should have already completed undergraduate studies and intend 
to pursue advanced studies in his/her original subject. He/She should be in 
good health and well behaved. If he/she is not capable of studying his/her 
specialized courses in Chinese, he/she is first expected to study Chinese for 
one year, and then continue his/her original studies after passing the HSK test. 
</DOC>
