<P>
<LI> 15. Computational Chemisty for Chemistry Educators <BR>
<A HREF="http://www.mcnc.org/HTML/ITD/NCSC/ccsyllabus.html">http://www.mcnc.org/HTML/ITD/NCSC/ccsyllabus.html</A>
<P>
<LI> 16. The Covis Project <BR>
<A HREF="http://www.covis.nwu.edu/info/covis-info.html">http://www.covis.nwu.edu/info/covis-info.html</A>
<P>
<LI> 17. Educational News Resources <BR>
<A HREF="http://www.bc.edu/bc_org/avp/soe/cihe/direct2/Ed.News.html">http://www.bc.edu/bc_org/avp/soe/cihe/direct2/Ed.News.html</A>
 <P>
<LI> 18. Mathematics <BR>
<A HREF="http://pegasus.cc.ucf.edu/~ucfcasio/casio.htm">http://pegasus.cc.ucf.edu/~ucfcasio/casio.htm</A>
