<header>
<title>Syllabus Conferences page</title>
</header>
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/sconf_bkground.gif"> 
<BODY LINK="#161BFF">




<center><font size="5">Syllabus Conferences</font></center>
<p>
<CENTER>Welcome to the Syllabus conference page where you'll find information on past and future conferences and seminars for faculty, administrators, and technology staff.</CENTER>
<p>
<HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=4 ALIGN=LEFT>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>Syllabus '97</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
