<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><A HREF="syll96HL.htm">Syllabus '96 Highlights</A></FONT></CENTER>

<P>

<center><font size="5"><A HREF="sconf96_cvr.html">Syllabus '96</A></font></center>
<center><font size="5">July 20-24, 1996</font></center>
<center><font size="5">Sonoma State University</font></center>
<p>
Due to the success of Syllabus '95, plans are already underway for <A HREF="sconf96_cvr.html">Syllabus '96</A> to be held at Sonoma this summer. The 1996 conference program will include expanded plenary sessions, more case study presentations, and a larger selection of <A HREF="sconf96_preconf.html">pre-conference workshops</A>. Also, the number of <A HREF="sconf96_exhibits.html">exhibts</A> and <A HREF="sconf96_exhibits.html">vendor</A> sessions will double.<br>
