<INPUT NAME="rs14" VALUE="14" TYPE=CHECKBOX>Reader Service #14<br>
<P>
<b>Waterloo Maple</b> offers Maple V-The Power Edition. It provides a suite of new features for problem-solving, technical word processing, and programming. <br>
<INPUT NAME="rs15" VALUE="15" TYPE=CHECKBOX>Reader Service #15<br>
<P>
<b>Wolfram Research</b> has recently released Mathematica 3.0, a fully integrated environment for technical computing. The new release introduces major new concepts in computation and presentation.<br>
<INPUT NAME="rs16" VALUE="16" TYPE=CHECKBOX>Reader Service #16<br>
<P>
<b>Xerox</b> offers the DocuTech Production Series, a modular family for production printing of up to 135 impressions per minute. The series enables faculty to cost-effectively reprint material on-demand. <br>
<INPUT NAME="rs17" VALUE="17" TYPE=CHECKBOX>Reader Service #17<br>






<P>
