<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>January Reader Service</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
Many of the products and advertisements in Syllabus are identified with a Reader Service number. To receive more information on specific products, simply check the corresponding numbers on this form, fill in your name and address and click the submit button.<BR>
<P>
