<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Syllabus '96 Exhibits and Technology Demonstrations</TITLE><!-- Date: Monday, December 25, 1995  2:20 PM --></HEAD><BODY BACKGROUND="images/sconf_bkground.gif"> <BODY LINK="#161BFF"><HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=4 ALIGN=LEFT><B>Exhibits and Technology Demonstrations</B><P>| <A HREF="sconf96_cvr.html">Syllabus '96 Cover</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_agenda.html">Syllabus '96 Agenda</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_preconf.html">Pre-Conference</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_mon.html">Monday</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_tues.html">Tuesday</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_wed.html">Wednesday</A> |<BR>| <A HREF="sconf96_faculty.html">Faculty and Presenters</A> | <BR>| <A HREF="sconf96_travel.html">Housing and Transportation</A> | <A HREF="sconf96_reg.html">Registration</A> |<P><A HREF="receive_credit_sconf96.htm">Receive Academic Credits for Attending Syllabus</A><HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=4 ALIGN=LEFT><P><FONT SIZE=6><B><CENTER>Syllabus '96</CENTER></B></FONT><FONT SIZE=6><B><CENTER> Exhibits and Technology Demonstrations</CENTER></B></FONT> <p><HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=4 ALIGN=LEFT><p>From multimedia to the Internet, Syllabus '96 promises to deliver the latest information on education technology through demonstrations and hands-on workshops. Presenters from leading technology companies will walk you through tips and tricks and show their newest products. Preview the latest education technologies including multimedia, quantitative tools, Internet products and services, and curriculum products.<P><BR><B><FONT SIZE=4>Syllabus '96 Technology Demonstration Sponsors</FONT></B><HR WIDTH=100% SIZE=4 ALIGN=LEFT><TABLE WIDTH=100% BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=5 CELLSPACING=1>  <TR>    <TD>Adobe Systems Inc.</TD>    <TD>Microsoft Corp.</TD>  </TR>  <TR>    <TD>Asymetrix Corp.</TD>    <TD>NETCOM On-Line<BR>Communication Corp.</TD>  </TR>  <TR>    <TD>Compresssion Labs Inc.</TD>    <TD>Panasonic Broadcast &<br>Television Systems Co.</TD>  </TR>  <TR>    <TD>Lotus Developme